items.description: Corporate earnings season takes off this week with U.S. banks led by JPMorgan Chase. Big companies outside of finance including Johnson & Johnson, Netflix and PepsiCo are also on the way. Here are the highlights of who is reporting, and the expected approximate release times.

items.title: Kenvue Yo-Yoes After Tylenol-Maker Unveils New CEO, Strategic Review
items.description: Kenvue stock yo-yoes Monday after the company — known for brands like Tylenol — announced a new CEO and strategic review.
